This is a '''bibliography of works about the [[Romanian Revolution]]'''.
The Romanian Revolution was a series of riots and clashes in December 1989. These were part of the [[Revolutions of 1989]] that occurred in several [[Warsaw Pact]] countries. The Romanian Revolution was the only one of these revolutions that forcibly overthrew a Communist government and executed the country's head of state.
